k>/docs/legal-hub/compliance/audit/internal-audit-nonconformity-report/</link><pubDate>Thu, 01 May 2025 21:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>/docs/legal-hub/compliance/audit/internal-audit-nonconformity-report/</guid><description/></item><item><title>Confidentiality Statement</title><link>/docs/legal-hub/compliance/audit/confidentiality-statement/</link><pubDate>Thu, 01 May 2025 20:58:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>/docs/legal-hub/compliance/audit/confidentiality-statement/</guid><description/></item><item><title>Corrective Action Report</title><link>/docs/legal-hub/compliance/audit/corrective-action-report/</link><pubDate>Thu, 01 May 2025 20:58:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>/docs/legal-hub/compliance/audit/corrective-action-report/</guid><description/></item><item><title>Monitoring And Measurement Plans</title><link>/docs/legal-hub/compliance/audit/monitoring-and-measurement-plans/</link><pubDate>Thu, 01 May 2025 20:22:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>/docs/legal-hub/compliance/audit/monitoring-and-measurement-plans/</guid><description/></item><item><title>Corrective Action Procedure (P Ca 05)</title><link>/docs/legal-hub/compliance/audit/corrective-action-procedure-p-ca-05/</link><pubDate>Thu, 01 May 2025 20:18:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>/docs/legal-hub/compliance/audit/corrective-action-procedure-p-ca-05/</guid><description/></item><item><title>Internal Audits And Management Reviews</title><link>/docs/legal-hub/compliance/audit/internal-audits-and-management-reviews/</link><pubDate>Wed, 30 Apr 2025 00:49:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>/docs/legal-hub/compliance/audit/internal-audits-and-management-reviews/</guid><description>&lt;h3 id="internal-audit-and-management-review-for-iso-50001">Internal Audit and Management Review for ISO 50001&lt;/h3>
&lt;p>The Internal Audit and Management Review processes are essential for ensuring that the Energy Management System (EnMS) is effectively implemented and continues to perform as required, in alignment with the ISO 50001:2018 standard. These processes enable continual improvement and ensure that energy performance is optimized, legal and regulatory compliance is maintained, and the energy management objectives are met.&lt;/p>
&lt;h3 id="1-internal-audit-for-iso-50001">1. Internal Audit for ISO 50001&lt;/h3>
&lt;p>The internal audit process ensures that the energy management system is functioning effectively, complying with the ISO 50001 standard, and meeting the organization&amp;rsquo;s energy goals. It provides a framework for identifying non-conformities, areas for improvement, and ensuring compliance with energy-related regulations.&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Internal Audit And Management Review Records</title><link>/docs/legal-hub/compliance/audit/internal-audit-and-management-review-records/</link><pubDate>Tue, 29 Apr 2025 17:09:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>/docs/legal-hub/compliance/audit/internal-audit-and-management-review-records/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="1-introduction">1. Introduction&lt;/h1>
&lt;p>This document outlines the framework for internal audits and management reviews at Green Orbit Digital, ensuring compliance with ISO standards and continuous improvement of our management systems.&lt;/p>
&lt;h2 id="2-internal-audit-framework">2. Internal Audit Framework&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>Internal audits are conducted to assess whether our management systems:&lt;/p>
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>
&lt;p>Conform to organizational requirements and ISO standards&lt;/p>
&lt;/li>
&lt;li>
&lt;p>Are effectively implemented and maintained&lt;/p>
&lt;/li>
&lt;li>
&lt;p>Support continuous improvement&lt;/p>
&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;h3 id="21-audit-methodology">2.1 Audit Methodology&lt;/h3>
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>
&lt;p>Document review&lt;/p>
&lt;/li>
&lt;li>
&lt;p>System testing&lt;/p>
&lt;/li>
&lt;li>
&lt;p>Process observation&lt;/p>
&lt;/li>
&lt;li>
&lt;p>Compliance verification&lt;/p>
&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;h3 id="22-documentation-review">2.2 Documentation Review&lt;/h3>
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>
&lt;p>Assessment of procedure manuals&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Internal Audit Programme And Reports</title><link>/docs/legal-hub/compliance/audit/internal-audit-programme-and-reports/</link><pubDate>Tue, 29 Apr 2025 17:09:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>/docs/legal-hub/compliance/audit/internal-audit-programme-and-reports/</guid><description/></item><item><title>Monitoring And Audit Records</title><link>/docs/legal-hub/compliance/audit/monitoring-and-audit-records/</link><pubDate>Tue, 29 Apr 2025 17:09:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>/docs/legal-hub/compliance/audit/monitoring-and-audit-records/</guid><description/></item><item><title>Monitoring And Measurement Records</title><link>/docs/legal-hub/compliance/audit/monitoring-and-measurement-records/</link><pubDate>Tue, 29 Apr 2025 17:09:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>/docs/legal-hub/compliance/audit/monitoring-and-measurement-records/</guid><description/></item><item><title>Confidentiality Audit</title><link>/docs/legal-hub/compliance/audit/confidentiality-audit/</link><pubDate>Thu, 24 Apr 2025 16:18:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>/docs/legal-hub/compliance/audit/confidentiality-audit/</guid><description/></item><item><title>Due Diligence</title><link>/docs/legal-hub/compliance/audit/due-diligence/</link><pubDate>Thu, 24 Apr 2025 16:18:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>/docs/legal-hub/compliance/audit/due-diligence/</guid><description/></item></channel></rss>